sequenceDiagram
    participant Citizen
    participant CBPortal as Child Benefit Portal
    participant IdentityResolution
    participant SemanticTranslation
    participant AwardCalculation
    participant Notification

    Note over Citizen: Sarah has DID from previous UC application
    Citizen->>CBPortal: Apply for Child Benefit using existing DID
    CBPortal->>IdentityResolution: POST /identity/correlate-dids (UC DID + CB context)
    IdentityResolution->>IdentityResolution: Analyze DID correlation evidence
    IdentityResolution-->>CBPortal: High confidence same person (0.92)
    
    Note over CBPortal: Offer evidence reuse
    CBPortal->>Citizen: "We found existing verified information. Use for Child Benefit?"
    Citizen->>CBPortal: Consent to reuse verified address, income, identity
    
    CBPortal->>SemanticTranslation: POST /semantic/translate (UC evidence to CB requirements)
    SemanticTranslation-->>CBPortal: Address valid, income meets CB threshold
    CBPortal->>Citizen: Only need birth certificate for new child
    
    Citizen->>CBPortal: Submit birth certificate
    CBPortal->>AwardCalculation: POST /awards/calculate (high confidence identity + new evidence)
    AwardCalculation-->>CBPortal: CB award calculated
    CBPortal->>Notification: POST /notifications/send (award approved)
    Notification->>Citizen: Child Benefit approved in 24 hours
    
    Note over Citizen,Notification: Same evidence reused across services while preserving policy differences
